B043C001V001	43	1	1	In a beginning was the Word, and the Word was with the God, and a god was the Word.
B043C001V002	43	1	2	This was in a beginning with the God.
B043C001V003	43	1	3	All through it was done; and without it was done not even one, that has been done.
B043C001V004	43	1	4	In it life was, and the life was the light of the men;
B043C001V005	43	1	5	and the light in the darkness shines, and the darkness it not apprehended.
