B043C001V043	43	1	43	The morrow he desired to go forth into the Galilee; and he finds Philip, and says to him: Follow me.
B043C001V044	43	1	44	Was and the Philip from Bethsaida of the city of Andrew and Peter.
B043C001V045	43	1	45	Finds Philip the Nathanael, and says to him: Whom wrote Moses in the law, and the prophets, we have found, Jesus the son of the Joseph, that from Nazareth.
B043C001V046	43	1	46	And said to him Nathanael: Out of Nazareth is able any good to be? Says to him Philip: Come and see.
